    "extras": [
      "Use the PID Lítačka app in Prague for the cheapest digital tram and metro tickets; the 24-hour pass is about ₹540 and the 72-hour pass is about ₹1,260.",
      "Mapy.cz is more reliable than generic map apps for Czech hiking paths, castle approaches, and offline navigation in smaller towns.",
      "Kutná Hora works well as an optional Prague day trip if you want Sedlec Ossuary and St. Barbara’s Cathedral without changing hotels.",
      "Avoid Euronet ATMs and use bank ATMs instead; cards are widely accepted, but carrying 500–1,000 CZK in cash helps in smaller towns.",
      "Book Villa Tugendhat tours, Prague Castle interiors, and Český Krumlov theatre slots ahead in summer because same-week inventory can vanish quickly.",
      "Vegetarian travelers should bookmark Lehká Hlava in Prague, Laibon in Cesky Krumlov, and VEGALITE in Brno before arrival."
